I"ˆ<h2 id="editorial">Editorial</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Write using <a href="https://www.plainlanguage.gov/guidelines/">plain language</a></li>
  <li>Follow 18Fâ€™s <a href="https://content-guide.18f.gov/our-style/inclusive-language/">inclusive language</a> style guide</li>
  <li>Write for a non-technical audience.</li>
  <li>Be concise</li>
  <li>Avoid acronyms or jargon</li>
  <li>Use active voice instead of passive voice</li>
  <li>Use descriptive links</li>
  <li>Avoid using footnotes</li>
</ul>

